### Recharts v3.0 Custom Component with Customized Prop

Source: https://github.com/recharts/recharts/wiki/3.0-migration-guide

This snippet shows one way to integrate a custom `MyCustomComponent` using the `Customized` wrapper in Recharts v3.0. While still supported, this method is now optional as v3.0 allows direct embedding of custom components. It illustrates a transitional approach to utilizing custom components within your charts.

```jsx
<BarChart width={1100} height={250} data={data}>
  <Customized component={MyCustomComponent} />
</BarChart>
```

